data.description: MUST SEE! A beautiful ranch on a full-finished basement with NO HOA! Move in ready! ONLY ONE OWNER! The roof and HVAC are only three years old. With three bedrooms and three full baths with an open-concept dining and large family room floor plan, you will love the space. Kitchen has a great flow with a bay window breakfast area. The finished basement is ready for all your entertaining and to keep family and friends relaxing and enjoying each gathering. The deck is perfect for those summer BBQs and quiet mornings. A fenced-in backyard is a great size and plenty of room to park your RV. Sitting on a corner lot, this property is fantastic!
